data.overView: By the end of the challenge, you'll have improved your fitness levels, built healthy habits, and gained a better understanding of your body's capabilities.Remember that this is a general overview, and you can customize the challenge based on your individual goals and preferences. Stay committed, stay motivated, and enjoy the process of transforming your fitness and well-being over the course of the month!

instructor.name: Josh Kramer
instructor.about: Josh is an international yoga teacher , who grew up in zimbabwe. he spend his youth in New zealand, where he developed his passion for yoga

videos.title: Day1 UPPER BODY STRENGTH
videos.description: Test Your Strength and Determination. This upper-body workout will condition your arms.

videos.title: Full Body HIIT Workout
videos.description: A high-intensity interval training (HIIT) session that targets your entire body for a quick and effective workout.

videos.title: Yoga for Flexibility
videos.description: Join this soothing yoga practice to improve your flexibility and promote relaxation.

videos.title: Cardio Kickboxing
videos.description: Get your heart pumping with this energetic cardio kickboxing routine that combines martial arts and cardio exercises.

videos.title: Lower Body Sculpting
videos.description: Focus on your lower body with this sculpting workout that targets your legs, glutes, and thighs.
